<br>
             - Words<br>
             - Runes<br>
             - Grimoire Pages (Tashan's, Velishoul's, Sali's, Nitilin's)<br>
             - Miscellaneous research items (Flame of Vox, Gloves of Solusek Ro, Globe of Fear, etc)<br>
<br>
If I have room, I will also put in any extra copies of spells that I research as Teynor (enchanter) or Crimsyn (necromancer), and if any other researchers want to add some spells in, I'll put that in too.<br>
<br>
In the next few days I will log on and make an inventory of everything that I have in the bank for research already and post it here.  If any of you ever need something from that list, let me know and I'll get it out and give it to ya.  However, this will only work if we all contribute, so please don't take a whole lot out if you never put anything in.<br>
<br>
Anytime you need something, just send me a tell in game and if I'm not dying TOO badly or off somewhere saving Aonedil &lt;whistles innocently&gt;, I'll grab it for ya.  Or you can post online here and I'll get it to you in game as soon as we can hook up.  NOTE:  This does not mean that I will run from Freeport to Emerald Jungle one day because you just HAVE to have that spell that night and can't stop smooshin whatever it is you're smooshin to come get it yourself.  :-)<br>
<br>
<br>
Hope this helps with research, I know it can be a major pain.<br>
<br>
<br>
Teynor Sax<br>
Enchanter of the 38th Monk buff<br>
<br>
P.S. - I will also research spells for any budding young 'chanters out there if you should need it (again, within reason...), so just send me a tell! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub30.ezboard.com/utaladan.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Taladan</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sentinent Member</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#333333>(1/29/01 4:49:36 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub30.ezboard.com/fthesentinentfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=149.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   OK .. I'll bite...</span><hr size=1> Been meanning to ask our Senior enchanters what Bedos will be needing to get into in the near future.  Still hovering around 16 and only figured out on Sat. why my new Mezmerization was hitting me .. duh .. it's an AoE!<br>
